@startuml UEORMS_State_07
top to bottom direction
hide empty description
title UEORMS State Transition - 7) CRM and Sales

[*] --> LeadCreated
LeadCreated --> LeadQualified : qualify lead
LeadQualified --> CustomerCreated : convert lead
CustomerCreated --> OpportunityOpen : create deal
OpportunityOpen --> QuotationDraft : create quotation
QuotationDraft --> QuotationSent : send quote
QuotationSent --> QuotationAccepted : accept quote
QuotationSent --> QuotationExpired : reject/expire
QuotationExpired --> QuotationDraft : revise quote
QuotationAccepted --> SalesOrderOpen : convert to order
SalesOrderOpen --> InvoiceGenerated : convert to invoice
InvoiceGenerated --> PaymentPending : await payment
PaymentPending --> PaymentReceived : payment posted
PaymentReceived --> OrderFulfilled : dispatch complete
OrderFulfilled --> AnalyticsUpdated : update analytics
AnalyticsUpdated --> [*]

@enduml
